titles: be careful what you wish for...
your desires, a curse in disguise...
you found a rotten hairy paw...
this was not meant for you...
this wasn’t meant to be found...
it was hidden for a reason...
you hold the weight of a curse...
it’s too late to turn back now...
what lies ahead cannot be undone...
a relic of regret in your hands...
the paw stirs in your hand...
you grasp what should be forgotten...
you’ve found something you shouldn’t have...
this is not a gift, it’s a trap...
